column5: Well its almost over and it was a super day.  Thanks again everyone for your birthday well wishes.  I appreciate them.  Joey
HAPPY BIRTHDAY
Happy Bday Joey hope ya had a great one  Cheers Mike
I definitely see a new musky rod in your future Joey, started working on it yesterday. Glad you had a "super" day.
Yeah, who needs a new stinkin' boat when you have one of Spiel's muskie sticks!
I want my avatar with you popping out of a cake (though the cooler is still "hot" )  HAPPY B-DAY JOEY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Happy Birthday you cutie you! Have the bestest day and tons more. I hope Paul bought you the boat you wanted for your BD....or at least something flimsey in leopard pattern.
Thanks Hon.  The boat is in the works, and I think maybe even a Spiel Custom Musky Rod!!!  As for the leopard, I guess we'll see
